<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Vérifiez votre boîte mail — SecurBox</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: #0f1117;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px;
            background: #161b27;
            border: 1px solid #2a2f3e;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .mail-icon-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .mail-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #6fbfff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6fbfff, #4dd4ac);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .search-badge {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            right: -5px;
            background: #0f1117;
            border: 2px solid #2a2f3e;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #4dd4ac;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        p {
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .email-highlight {
            color: #6fbfff;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .btn-back {
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-back:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="email-container">
    <div class="mail-icon-wrapper">
        <i class="fas fa-envelope-open-text mail-icon"></i>
        <div class="search-badge">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <h1>Vérifiez vos e-mails</h1>
    
    <p>Suivez le lien contenu dans l'e-mail envoyé à <br><span class="email-highlight">{{ userEmail }}</span> pour continuer la création de votre compte.</p>
    
    <hr style="border-color: #2a2f3e; margin: 24px 0;">
    
    <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="btn-back">
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-1"></i> Modifier l'adresse e-mail
    </a>
</div>

</body>
</html>